description:
My friends and I headed to Napa Valley to check out vegan cookbook author, Isa Chandra Moskowitz in her four-city cooking tour called "Isa Live: A Vegan Life in Four Courses".

Isa's event was at night so my friends and I decided to drive early in the afternoon to grab lunch and check out the vegan scene. Apparently, there's not a lot (surprise, surprise) but we still made the most out our trip and took advantage of all the vegan options of the places we visited. Please check the links below to learn more about them.

Places:
Melted http://www.meltednapavalley.com/
Oxbow Public Market http://oxbowpublicmarket.com/
City Winery http://www.citywinery.com/napa/

For my full review, please visit my blog: http://astigvegan.com

Music: "Cut Your Teeth (Kygo Remix)" by Kyla La Grange

Thanks for watching!
